				Font Enhancement: Class Default
				Text Color: Class Default
				Background Color: Class Default
			Background Text: It is highly advisable that no one else work with the order tables, as they will timeout the rollover.
				Resource Id: 36730
				Class Child Ref Key: 0
				Class ChildKey: 0
				Class: clsBackTextGeneral
				Window Location and Size
					Left:   0.763"
