			Background Text: It is also recommended that all other users be warned about the systems slow response during rollover.
				Resource Id: 36718
				Class Child Ref Key: 0
				Class ChildKey: 0
				Class: clsBackTextGeneral
				Window Location and Size
					Left:   0.763"
					Top:    1.854"
